{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was just-- as I tell it to you now, it's difficult for me to even describe it, because it was happening on a, on a minute-to-minute situation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I got into the-- i got this line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was this big line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I saw my mother on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was another side, where the women went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I, I never saw her cry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't-- I never saw her reach out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She just-- the last time I saw, she was hanging on to my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my dad hollered to her, you hang-- you take care of her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'll take care of him, in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And whatever we have to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was the last word I heard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my dad threw me in front of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he says, keep walking very tall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Don't even-- because we were observing what was going on in the front-- you know, in the front of the lines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the very-- the one thing you didn't want is for the Germans to see that you were holding on to your child, because that was the whole idea, is to break up the family, murder the family.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was the genocide of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So by not identifying that this is your child, there was a little bit of an edge you had to possibly survive, the fact that you are on your own and you sort of didn't belong to any family.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "By some miracle-- and, again, I tell you that this is, this was so fast and so incredibly-- within minutes I see these Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there was all commands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I just-- I couldn't understand any of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[GERMAN], you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Today, of course, I know I learned to speak German because I had to.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
